{
  "stem": "33.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we looked at each other after our heads were shaved.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We could hardly recognize one another.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I think it was sort of like some kind of a really hysterical laughter.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We just started to laugh like it was an uncontrollable thing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was the shock, probably.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were given one piece of garment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I remember I had a blue-- some kind of miserable dress.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we were given a pair of panties.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that was about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We kept our shoes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Not everybody did, but I think at that point, that group, we kept our shoes, but no stockings or anything and nothing else.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "That was the three pieces, shoes, pair of panties, and a dress.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we were taken into the camps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "One of the first things that they made us do was we were each given a postcard.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we had to write that postcard to a non-Jewish neighbor or friend or schoolmate, whoever.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we all had to write the same thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We had to write that we arrived to camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We are working.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We are together, meaning the families.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we're doing well.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They did keep up this charade.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I mean, it didn't matter that it was June the 3rd of 1944.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I don't suppose that even the most fanatical Nazi could have had any hopes still of winning the war, but they did keep it up.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We were taken into barracks where we slept.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Some of the barracks had nothing but a bare floor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "The one that I was taken to had three-story bunk beds.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They were double beds, nothing except the hard board.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "No pillow, no straw, no mattress, no blanket, absolutely nothing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Seven of us slept on one of these double beds.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
